      "content": "the professional advice thing feels like a joke right now. i've spent years building this, everyone believed in me, and now i'm just a guy who lost everything. the shame is what's killing me. i feel like everyone is just waiting for me to fail, and honestly, i've already failed. there's no \"taking a step back\" from this level of humiliation. it's like the person i was is just dead anyway.",
